  "NAME=DH0,DH1,DH2,*.device". You can use * as a wildcard.

@{B}USER@{UB}

  Template:  U=USER/K
  Tooltype:  USER

  Names of the users whose every task's nice-value will be incremented.
  You can list multiple user names here, separate them with a comma, for
