  Template:  O=OUTPUT/K
  Tooltype:  OUTPUT

  This is used to redirect the output of Timer to a file.
  For example:

    @{"Timer OUTPUT=T:timer.out dir" SYSTEM "Timer OUTPUT=T:timer.out STDOUT dir >CON:0/0/640/200/Output/CLOSE/WAIT"}

